text: Adriana Serra Zanetti and Antonella Serra Zanetti were the defending champions, but chose not to participate that year. Maria Elena Camerin and Émilie Loit won in the final 6–3, 6–0 against Anastasia Rodionova and Galina Voskoboeva. ==Seeds== # Maria Elena Camerin / Émilie Loit (Champions) # Emmanuelle Gagliardi / María Emilia Salerni (First Round) # Caroline Dhenin / Mara Santangelo (First Round) # Klaudia Jans / Alicja Rosolska (First Round) ==Draw== ==References== ==External links== * Main and Qualifying Draws Singles Tashkent Open Category:2005 in Uzbekistani sport
